{
  "texts": [
    "In this way we findTheorem 2.",
    "3.23The irreducible anyon sectors with respect to the vacuum representation of the Levin-Wen model over C are in one-to-one correspondence with equivalence classes of simple objects of the Drinfeld center Z(C).",
    "S(Σ; b) denote the set of all string diagrams on Σ with boundary condition b.",
    "We define A(Σ; b):= C[S(Σ; b)]/ ∼, the space of all finite formal C-linear combinations of string diagrams on Σ with boundary condition b, modded out by the equivalence relation ∼ generated by • isotopy of string diagrams in Σ keeping ∂Σ fixed.",
    "let ∂ b (N × I) = ( N × {0}) be the bottom and ∂ t (N × I) = (N × {1}) the top of the decorated surface N × I."
  ]
}